	<string>Advance Github Search

Type `gh` (full GitHub search) or `gm` (restricted to user:{var:github_user}) and pick from the menu:
- Github Search ...   → search the query as-is
- option: extension   → extension picker (ts, kt, md, ...)
- option: filename    → filename (path:**/&lt;value&gt;)
- option: path        → path (path:&lt;value&gt;)
- option: language    → language picker (ts, kt, md, ...)
- option: symbol      → symbol (function / class name)

Flow:
1. `gh` or `gm` → pick option
2-a. Github Search: enter query → opens GitHub Code Search results
2-b. language / extension: pick from list → enter query (optional) → opens results
2-c. other options: enter value → enter query (optional) → opens results

Configure the GitHub username under "Configure Workflow…".</string>
